    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>butternut squash cubes </strong>to one side of a separate <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray with your<strong> sage</strong> (chuck it in, stalks and all!), a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for an initial 12 min – this is your <strong>sage roasted squash</strong></p>",
